to reiterate what i said in my previous posting dated 12 6 2012 they have the very best GOODREVIEW grilled chicken pita you will ever eat i have eaten this same item at numerous greek owned restaurants showmars nikkos grill mr g s maxwell s tavern in waxhaw athenian grill in indian trail etc yet no one can come close to the flavor of this one it s all about the way they marinate their chicken as well as the tzatziki sauce and lettuce that they use the pita also has onion and tomatoes as well do yourself a favor try theirs and then compare to any others in charlotte and surrounding area and you will understand what i mean
